s=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇野睇咁表面。</blockquote>成班不願面對現實<br />\n俾20年所謂中國強大洗腦</blockquote>商學院院長都係被迫咁寫<br />\n美國有幾多資產唔通同你講&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逼？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛唔飲水唔㩒得牛頭低，西唔插深唔屌得西水流！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d0f8ba4ea723333a82a1f9fd5bebf6170ac4d7ae","tid":971790,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5毛真好笑<br />\n<br />\n又係財經台個D,係咁問美國出招未個班"},{"pid":"942d2c383710704c6a92c6efbc6a3d5d72df6163","tid":971790,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T03:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a322145238479f8aae0db52dc0e973b1e39f10","tid":971790,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"今日睇啲財演話咩2020大選<br />\ntrump 會暫緩貿易戰粉飾太平<br />\n所以睇好股市升<br />\n真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"6a048e2bd6bdb0eb202b1a5b1b2386f2beee493e","tid":971790,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c402be99f6548da8976d0c13cf79cb0c5d423ca6","tid":971790,"uid":117679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"美國擺明借貿易戰，嚟推冧中國經濟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令佢地唔好妄想可以同美國比天下。<br />\n<br />\n如果單單只係為咗消除貿易逆差問題，彭斯就唔會係上年年尾講咁大篇中國威脅論出嚟啦。<br />\n<br />\n仲話係商學院院長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇野睇咁表面。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"篇野仲要專登翻譯定做殘體字驚死你睇唔明"},{"pid":"f41b77ba99e303186045b9bfcd64f8c1aa5ff9ab","tid":971790,"uid":117679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a0a322145238479f8aae0db52dc0e973b1e39f10","tid":971790,"uid":31186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"今日睇啲財演話咩2020大選<br />\ntrump 會暫緩貿易戰粉飾太平<br />\n所以睇好股市升<br />\n真係得啖笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實，班友係唔係已經唔記得咗當年美國總統選舉啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰陣大家幾撚驚「民主黨」嘅希拉莉做到總統。驚佢搞鳩南中國海，回歸亞太區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當侵侵選到總統，大家幾撚興奮，好似自己有得選咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點撚知，侵侵就搞鳩咗中共。<br />\n<br />\n依家班友唔係覺得侵侵落咗台，美國就唔會搞鳩中共吓嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事實係邊撚個做美國總統，都係會搞鳩你中共。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼叫你習大帝咁撚聰明，當美國冇到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好無知啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b8792a8a68d8b34e8d595603ee3ea89e838e40","tid":971790,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d86c689a65569a8d84a341f771db37fd86ec966","tid":971790,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"有此等良才，何愁中共不射？"},{"pid":"fd1581fb5cf83e33569f0da2fed3bb57f734c602","tid":971790,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"何濼生當年比教主屌到一棟都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"htt